            <h1>AN OUTCYCLING CLUB FOR YOUNG ADULTS AGES 16-21</h1><hr>
               <span id="flyers-goal">OUR GOAL: </span><span>To build self-confidence, leadership and cycling skills in young adults.</span>
            <h1>WHY JOIN THE FEARLESS FLYERS in 2017?</h1>
               
                    <ul>
                        <li>EARN A BRAND NEW BICYCLE AND HELMET & LOCK FOR FREE.</li>
                        <li>Build your fitness strength, and endurance with other LGBT (QQIA) young adults.</li>
                        <li>Become more self-confident as an individual and a supportive team member.</li>
                        <li>Explore the best city in the world: NYC!</li>
                    </ul>
               <h1>WHAT AM I SIGNING UP FOR?</h1>
               <p>Fearless Flyers is a spring cycling program designed for bide-riders of all fitness levels. Each member will be provided with a bike and equipment, safety and skills workshops, and Saturday morning training rides to prepare for the <%= link_to 'NYC Pride Ride', 'http://www.nycprideride.org', target:'_blank', style:"color:rgba(10,151,255,1)" %>.</p>
               
               <div id="youthdates">
                <h2>MANDATORY MEETINGS: (MEMBERS MUST COMPLETE TO EARN A BIKE)</h2>
                   <p>Get fit. Pre-Training with Shape Up NYC:<br>-Saturdays: March 4, 11, 18, 26</p>
                <h2>SPRING TRAINING RIDES: (MEMBERS MUST COMPLETE AT LEAST 7 TO EARN A BIKE)</h2>
                   <p>-Saturdays: April 1. 8, 15, 22, May 6, 13, 20, 27, June 3<br>-Sunday: June 11 NYC Pride Ride</p>
                <h2>ALL WORKSHOPS & TRAINING RIDES MEET AT:</h2>   
                   <p>Al's Cycle Solution - 693 Tenth Ave. (btw 47th & 48th Street) @ 9:30am SHARP</p>  
               </div>
               
               <h1>HOW DO I JOIN FEARLESS FLYERS?</h1>
                    <p>1. You must be a NYC resident age 16-21.</p>
                    <p>2. You must already know how to ride a bike and be in good physical health.</p>
               <p>3. Complete and submit the <%=link_to "Fearless Flyers Application", '/riders/new', style:"color: rgba(10,151,255,1)" %> by February 28th.</p>
                    <hr>
               <p id="flyer-questions">For any questions, please contact Graham Weinstein at graham@outcycling.org<br>Outcycling, Inc. 115 west 18th Street, 2nd floor, New York, NY 10011 - <%= link_to 'Outcycling.org', "http://www.outcycling.org", style:"color: rgba(10,151,255,1)" %></p>
                   
               
           </div> 
            
